      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * TRATTAMENTO REGISTRAZIONE SCADENZE                        *
      *    *===========================================================*
      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione si/no corpo 3 da trattare                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       snp-co3-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di uscita a Si                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-imp-snp      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se gestione scadenze fornitore attiva      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-scf-snx        =    "S" and
                     w-prs-snx-scf        =    "S"
                     go to snp-co3-reg-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag di uscita a No                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-imp-snp      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiustamento status impostazioni corpo 3   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-imp-co3      .
       snp-co3-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione corpo 3 a partire dalla riga con numero      *
      *    * d'ordine : w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-co3-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione tipo uscita da corpo            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Caricamento catena scadenze fornitore           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non da effettuare : oltre                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-co3-fdc-scf (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-010.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo routine                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   car-cat-scf-000      thru car-cat-scf-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiornamento flag di caricamento righe mo- *
      *                  * vimento contabile                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-co3-fdc-scf (1)      .
       acc-co3-reg-010.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Confronto tra numero d'ordine riga da accettare *
      *              * e numero d'ordine dell'ultima riga              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    not  > w-cat-rg3-max
                     go to acc-co3-reg-025.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se oltre numero riga massimo e Append non pos-  *
      *              * sibile si esce con status di uscita "+"         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-app        not  = spaces
                     move  "+"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3
                     go to acc-co3-reg-990.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se oltre numero riga massimo e Append possibile *
      *              * si esegue l'operazione di Append                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg3-max        to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           move      "AP"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-025.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in 'OFF'                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prompts per corpo                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-pmt-co3    =    spaces
                     perform pmt-co3-reg-000
                                          thru pmt-co3-reg-999
                     move    "#"          to   w-cnt-sts-pmt-co3      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione dati corpo                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione nr pagina da visualizzare    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav      .
           add       w-ln3-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav      .
           divide    w-ln3-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non e' visualizzata nessuna pagina corpo *
      *                  * o una pagina corpo diversa da quella da vi- *
      *                  * sualizzare si procede alla visualizzazione  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-vis-co3    =    spaces           or
                     w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis    not  = w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav
                     perform vis-co3-reg-000
                                          thru vis-co3-reg-999
                     move    "#"          to   w-cnt-sts-vis-co3
                     move    w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura riga da catena                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RD"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
           move      w-cat-rg3-buf        to   w-rg3                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se riga nuova si normalizza il corpo            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-050.
           perform   nor-nok-rg3-000      thru nor-nok-rg3-999        .
           move      w-rg3-val-aep (1)    to   w-rg3-val-aep (2)      .
       acc-co3-reg-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Routine pre-accettazione riga corpo             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pre-rig-co3-000      thru pre-rig-co3-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione prompts per riga d'accettazione *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-rig-co3-000      thru pmt-rig-co3-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione dati per riga di accettazione   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-rig-co3-000      thru vis-rig-co3-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in 'ON'                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di status impostazione corpo               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-max        =    zero
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-sts-imp-co3
           else      move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-co3      .
           if        w-cat-rg3-max        =    1        and
                     w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        not  = spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-sts-imp-co3      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di status impostione riga attuale          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-sts-imp-rg3
           else      move  spaces         to   w-cnt-sts-imp-rg3      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Indicatore linea in corso di trattamento        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "I"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione tipo uscita da riga corpo       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3      .
       acc-co3-reg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazioni                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo impostazione : primo campo riga corpo  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "C"                  to   w-cnt-mfu-tip-imp      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo riga per scadenza fornitore            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tri-scf-000      thru acc-tri-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-925.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo impostazione : altri campi riga corpo  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-mfu-tip-imp      .
       acc-co3-reg-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione func-key di impostazione    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/no pagamento bloccato                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-snx-pbl-000      thru acc-snx-pbl-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
       acc-co3-reg-225.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data scadenza                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-dts-scf-000      thru acc-dts-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-200.
       acc-co3-reg-250.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importo in valuta scadenza fornitore        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-iiv-scf-000      thru acc-iiv-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-225.
       acc-co3-reg-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importo scadenza fornitore                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-imp-scf-000      thru acc-imp-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-250.
       acc-co3-reg-350.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Nostra banca d'appoggio per scadenza forni- *
      *                  * tore                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cbp-scf-000      thru acc-cbp-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-300.
       acc-co3-reg-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice ABI banca per scadenza fornitore     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-abi-scf-000      thru acc-abi-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-350.
       acc-co3-reg-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice CAB sportello per scadenza fornitore *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cab-scf-000      thru acc-cab-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-400.
       acc-co3-reg-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * C/C bancario per scadenza fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ccc-scf-000      thru acc-ccc-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-450.
       acc-co3-reg-550.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * C/C postale per scadenza fornitore          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-ccp-scf-000      thru acc-ccp-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-500.
       acc-co3-reg-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Banca estera per scadenza fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-bef-scf-000      thru acc-bef-scf-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-co3-reg-550.
       acc-co3-reg-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo finale su riga impostata              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cnt-tdo-rg3-000      thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg    not  = spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                     move  "UP  "         to   v-key
                     go to acc-co3-reg-200.
       acc-co3-reg-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tests per uscita significativa da interno riga  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    spaces or
                     w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "S"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-905
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "R"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-910.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Exit da interno riga                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga New funzionamento come per Remv *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-915.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga non New                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione numero riga         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-905.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Do da interno riga                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record di tipo New attribuzione del  *
      *                      * numero progressivo per la riga          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-907.
           perform   prg-rig-co3-000      thru prg-rig-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-907.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Routine post-accettazione riga          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tip-agg      .
           perform   pos-rig-co3-000      thru pos-rig-co3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Update riga in catena movimenti         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "UP"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           move      w-rg3                to   w-cat-rg3-buf          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Visualizzazione linea corpo             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Incremento del numero d'ordine della    *
      *                      * riga da accettare                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-910.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Remv da interno riga                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga non new : routine post-accetta- *
      *                      * zione riga                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-915.
           move      "-"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tip-agg      .
           perform   pos-rig-co3-000      thru pos-rig-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-915.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Visualizzazione numero riga a spaces se *
      *                      * si e' in Append                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        not  = spaces
                     move    "S"          to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig
                     move    w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav
                     perform vis-lin-co3-000
                                          thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata *
      *                      * a zero per forzare la rivisualizzazione *
      *                      * a meno che non si sia in Append         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rimozione record dalla catena           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Segnale di almeno una modifica          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-acc-flg-aum      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-925.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tests per uscita significativa dal primo campo  *
      *              * di impostazione della riga                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "U"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-935
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "D"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-940
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "S"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-945
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "X"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-950
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "I"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-955
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "R"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-960
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "T"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-965
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "B"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-970
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "N"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-975
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "P"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-980
           else if   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3    =    "."
                     go to acc-co3-reg-985.
       acc-co3-reg-930.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Exit da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "E"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-990.
       acc-co3-reg-935.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Up da primo campo di impostazione riga   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-936.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces se si e' in Append           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        not  = spaces
                     move    "S"          to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig
                     move    w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav
                     perform vis-lin-co3-000
                                          thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione,  a meno che non si sia  *
      *                          * in Append                           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-937.
       acc-co3-reg-936.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-937.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si e' sulla riga numero 1        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    =    1
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3
                     go to acc-co3-reg-990.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se non si e' sulla riga numero 1    *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-940.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Down da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-941.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si e' in Append si prepara il    *
      *                          * tipo uscita "+" e si visualizza il  *
      *                          * numero riga a spaces                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        not  = spaces
                     move    "+"          to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3
                     move    "S"          to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig
                     move    w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav
                     perform vis-lin-co3-000
                                          thru vis-lin-co3-999
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Altrimenti si prepara il numero pa- *
      *                          * gina attualmente visualizzata a ze- *
      *                          * ro per forzare la rivisualizzazione *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           else      move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si era in Append : uscita        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-co3    =    "+"
                     go to acc-co3-reg-990
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Altrimenti : riciclo                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           else      go to acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-941.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Incremento del numero riga          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-945.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Do da primo campo di impostazione riga   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-946.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-946.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-990.
       acc-co3-reg-950.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Delt da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-951.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-951.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "X"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-990.
       acc-co3-reg-955.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Insr da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Inserimento record nella catena         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "IN"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero pagina attualmente  visualizzata *
      *                      * a zero per forzare la rivisualizzazione *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-960.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Remv da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga non new : routine post-accetta- *
      *                      * zione riga                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-962.
           move      "-"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tip-agg      .
           perform   pos-rig-co3-000      thru pos-rig-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-962.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se in Append : visualizzazione del nu-  *
      *                      * mero riga a spaces                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        not  = spaces
                     move    "S"          to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig
                     move    w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav
                     perform vis-lin-co3-000
                                          thru vis-lin-co3-999
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Altrimenti si prepara il numero pagina  *
      *                      * attualmente visualizzata a zero per     *
      *                      * forzare la rivisualizzazione            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           else      move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Rimozione record dalla catena           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Segnale di almeno una modifica          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-acc-flg-aum      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-965.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Tab da primo campo di impostazione riga  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-966.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-967.
       acc-co3-reg-966.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-967.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Ad accettazione max + 1             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg3-max        to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           if        w-cat-rg3-app        =    spaces
                     add   1              to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-970.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Back da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-971.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
           move      1                    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-971.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
           move      1                    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-975.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Nxsc da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-976.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-977.
       acc-co3-reg-976.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-977.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si era nell'ultima riga, ed essa *
      *                          * era in Append : tipo uscita "+" e   *
      *                          * si esce                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    >    w-cat-rg3-max
                     move    "+"          to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3
                     go to acc-co3-reg-990.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione numero d'ordine del- *
      *                          * la prima riga appartenente alla pa- *
      *                          * gina (max + 1)                      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg3-max        to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           add       w-ln3-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           divide    w-ln3-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           multiply  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Determinazione numero d'ordine del- *
      *                          * la prima riga appartenente alla pa- *
      *                          * gina (attuale + 1)                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       w-ln3-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           divide    w-ln3-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           multiply  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se la prossima pagina e' sicuramen- *
      *                          * te prima dell'ultima                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    <    w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001
                     move  w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                     go to acc-co3-reg-000.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si e' sull'ultima pagina la qua- *
      *                          * le e' pero' completamente piena     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           if        w-cat-rg3-max        =    w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001
                     move  w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002
                                          to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                     go to acc-co3-reg-000.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si supera l'ultima pagina        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "+"                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-990.
       acc-co3-reg-980.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Prsc da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-981.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-982.
       acc-co3-reg-981.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-982.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se si e' sulla prima pagina         *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    not  > w-ln3-num-lin-vis
                     move  "-"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-co3
                     go to acc-co3-reg-990.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se non si e' sulla prima pagina     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    from w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           divide    w-ln3-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           multiply  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-985.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se Slct da primo campo di impostazione riga *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record New                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-co3-reg-986.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga a   *
      *                          * spaces                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Numero pagina attualmente visualiz- *
      *                          * zata a zero per forzare la rivisua- *
      *                          * lizzazione a meno che non si sia in *
      *                          * Append                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  zero           to   w-cnt-co3-nrp-vis      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rimozione record dalla catena       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "RM"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il numero riga di destinazione   *
      *                          * risulta oltre il numero d'ordine    *
      *                          * attuale si sottrae 1 al numero ri-  *
      *                          * ga di destinazione                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-slc-num-rig    >    w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                     subtract  1          from w-cnt-slc-num-rig      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-987.
       acc-co3-reg-986.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non New                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione del numero riga     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
       acc-co3-reg-987.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Ad accettazione nr riga selezionato *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-slc-num-rig    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac      .
           go to     acc-co3-reg-000.
       acc-co3-reg-990.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assestamento status di impostazione corpo       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-imp-co3      .
       acc-co3-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione pagina corpo 3 numero : w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-co3-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattini verticali                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "                                       |          
      -              "                             |"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      09                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      10                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-co3-reg-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero d'ordine del primo numero *
      *              * riga da visualizzare                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrp-dav    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           multiply  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
           subtract  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero d'ordine dell'ultimo nu-  *
      *              * mero riga da visualizzare                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
           add       w-ln3-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Operazione di Start su catena movimenti         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cat-rg3-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start errata : fine visualizzazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-co3-reg-999.
       vis-co3-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale catena movimenti            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rg3-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-ct3-000      thru cll-sub-ct3-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se fine lettura : fine visualizzazione      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-co3-reg-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work di  *
      *              * lavoro                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg3-buf        to   w-rg3                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riga singolo movimento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig      .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    to   w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav      .
           perform   vis-lin-co3-000      thru vis-lin-co3-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento numero riga da visualizzare          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se oltre ultima riga da visualizzare       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-008    not  > w-cnt-wrk-ctr-009
                     go to vis-co3-reg-200.
       vis-co3-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione linea corpo 3 numero : w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-lin-co3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero linea assoluta a video    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           add       w-ln3-num-lin-vis    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           divide    w-ln3-num-lin-vis    into w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           multiply  w-ln3-num-lin-vis    by   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           subtract  w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001    from w-cnt-co3-nrg-dav
                                        giving w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           add       w-ln3-pri-lin-vid    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero posizione assoluta a vi-  *
      *              * deo                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      01                   to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiustamento numero linea e posizione nel caso *
      *              * la linea debba essere visualizzata nella parte  *
      *              * destra                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    >    12
                     subtract 7           from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002
                     move     41          to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo visualizzazione riga               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig    =    "I"
                     go to vis-lin-co3-100
           else if   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig    =    "S"
                     go to vis-lin-co3-200
           else if   w-cnt-co3-tvi-rig    =    "N"
                     go to vis-lin-co3-300
           else      go to vis-lin-co3-400.
       vis-lin-co3-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione indicatore linea         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "=>"                 to   w-ln3-imm-num-lin      .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-co3-900.
       vis-lin-co3-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione numero linea a spaces    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-ln3-imm-num-lin      .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           go to     vis-lin-co3-900.
       vis-lin-co3-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione numero d'ordine riga     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rg3-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-ln3-imm-num-lin      .
           go to     vis-lin-co3-900.
       vis-lin-co3-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se visualizzazione riga intera              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga in append : uscita              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        not  = spaces
                     go to  vis-lin-co3-999.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Abblencamento immagine linea di corpo   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-ln3-imm              .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing Numero d'ordine riga            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-cat-rg3-cur        to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-ln3-imm-num-lin      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga di tipo New : fine editing      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces
                     go to vis-lin-co3-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing tipo scadenza                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    01
                     move  "Rim.Diretta"
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    02
                     move  "Inc.Elettr."
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    03
                     move  "Ri.Ba.     "
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    04
                     move  "C.d.O.     "
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    05
                     move  "M.Av.      "
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    06
                     move  "R.I.D.     "
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    07
                     move  "Bonif.Banc."
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    08
                     move  "C/C Postale"
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    09
                     move  "Ricev.Banc."
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    10
                     move  "Tratta     "
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    11
                     move  "Paghero'   "
                                          to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf
           else      move  spaces         to   w-ln3-imm-tip-scf      .
       vis-lin-co3-600.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing data scadenza                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    =    zero
                     go to vis-lin-cor-605
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-610.
       vis-lin-cor-605.
           move      " A vista"           to   w-ln3-imm-dts-scf      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-625.
       vis-lin-cor-610.
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    to   v-dat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-ln3-imm-dts-scf      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-625.
       vis-lin-cor-625.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing importo scadenza                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "G"                  to   v-edm                  .
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     move  w-rg3-imp-scf (1)
                                          to   v-num
           else      move  w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)
                                          to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-ln3-imm-imp-scf      .
       vis-lin-co3-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Parametri per visualizzazione           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      39                   to   v-car                  .
       vis-lin-co3-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione visualizzazione                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002    to   v-lin                  .
           move      w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001    to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-ln3-imm            to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-lin-co3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts area linee di corpo 3             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-co3-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      15                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Fincatura                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "NR     Tipo    Scadenza     Importo    |NR     Tip
      -              "o    Scadenza     Importo    |"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sottolineatura fincatura                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "-- ----------- -------- ---------------|-- -------
      -              "---- -------- ---------------|"
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Linea di trattini                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all "-"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Prompts per totale                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Totale in valuta scadenze fornitore     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tiv-scf-000      thru pmt-tiv-scf-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Totale scadenze fornitore               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tot-scf-000      thru pmt-tot-scf-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valori per totale                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Totale in valuta scadenze fornitore     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tiv-scf-000      thru vis-tiv-scf-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Totale scadenze fornitore               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-scf-000      thru vis-tot-scf-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Linea di trattini                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      15                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all "-"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-co3-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Totale scadenze fornitore in valuta          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tiv-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da visualizzare                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pmt-tiv-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Literal                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Totale           :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sigla valuta                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      15                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-tiv-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Totale scadenze fornitore                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tot-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda della sigla valuta         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pmt-tot-scf-100
           else      go to pmt-tot-scf-200.
       pmt-tot-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se sigla valuta pari a quella base              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Totale  scadenze :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-tot-scf-999.
       pmt-tot-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se sigla valuta diversa da quella base          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      37                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "In    :"            to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      40                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      c-sgl                to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-tot-scf-999.
       pmt-tot-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione riga corpo 3 di accettazione in w-rg3     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-rig-co3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se riga di tipo New : nessuna visualizzazione   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        not  = spaces
                     go to vis-rig-co3-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo riga                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tri-scf-000      thru vis-tri-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/No pagamento bloccato                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-snx-pbl-000      thru vis-snx-pbl-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data scadenza fornitore                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-dts-scf-000      thru vis-dts-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo in valuta scadenza fornitore            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-iiv-scf-000      thru vis-iiv-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo scadenza fornitore                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-imp-scf-000      thru vis-imp-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Nostra banca d'appoggio per scadenza fornitore  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cbp-scf-000      thru vis-cbp-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-cbp-scf-des-000  thru vis-cbp-scf-des-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice ABI banca per scadenza fornitore         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-abi-scf-000      thru vis-abi-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-abi-scf-den-000  thru vis-abi-scf-den-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice CAB sportello per scadenza fornitore     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cab-scf-000      thru vis-cab-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-cab-scf-den-000  thru vis-cab-scf-den-999    .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * C/C bancario per scadenza fornitore             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ccc-scf-000      thru vis-ccc-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * IBAN per scadenza fornitore                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ibn-scf-000      thru vis-ibn-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * C/C postale per scadenza fornitore              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ccp-scf-000      thru vis-ccp-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Banca estera per scadenza fornitore             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-bef-scf-000      thru vis-bef-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-bef-scf-des-000  thru vis-bef-scf-des-999    .
           perform   vis-bef-scf-fil-000  thru vis-bef-scf-fil-999    .
           perform   vis-bef-scf-ccc-000  thru vis-bef-scf-ccc-999    .
       vis-rig-co3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts per riga corpo 3 di accettazione  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-rig-co3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo riga per scadenze fornitori                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tri-scf-000      thru pmt-tri-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/No pagamento bloccato                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-snx-pbl-000      thru pmt-snx-pbl-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data scadenza fornitore                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dts-scf-000      thru pmt-dts-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo in valuta scadenza fornitore            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-iiv-scf-000      thru pmt-iiv-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo scadenza fornitore                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-imp-scf-000      thru pmt-imp-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Appoggio scadenza fornitore                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-app-scf-000      thru pmt-app-scf-999        .
       pmt-rig-co3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Tipo riga per scadenze fornitore             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-tri-scf-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Tipo scadenza    :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-tri-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Si/No pagamento bloccato                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-snx-pbl-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      17                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      60                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Pagam. bloccato :"  to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-snx-pbl-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Data scadenza                                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-dts-scf-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Data scadenza    :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-dts-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Importo scadenza fornitore                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-iiv-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se da visualizzare                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pmt-iiv-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Literal                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Importo          :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Sigla valuta                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      15                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       pmt-iiv-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Importo scadenza fornitore                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-imp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda della sigla valuta         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pmt-imp-scf-100
           else      go to pmt-imp-scf-200.
       pmt-imp-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se sigla valuta pari a quella base              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Importo scadenza :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-imp-scf-999.
       pmt-imp-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se sigla valuta diversa da quella base          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      37                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "In    :"            to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      40                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      c-sgl                to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-imp-scf-999.
       pmt-imp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt per : Appoggio scadenza fornitore                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-app-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo scadenza        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    01
                     go to pmt-app-scf-100
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    02 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    03 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    04 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    05 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    06
                     go to pmt-app-scf-200
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    07
                     go to pmt-app-scf-300
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    08
                     go to pmt-app-scf-400
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    09 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    10 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    11
                     go to pmt-app-scf-200
           else      go to pmt-app-scf-999.
       pmt-app-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 01                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Nessun prompt                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-app-scf-999.
       pmt-app-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 02, 03, 04, 05, 06, 09, 10,  *
      *              *                    11                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Ns. banca        :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-app-scf-999.
       pmt-app-scf-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 07                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del tipo valuta sca- *
      *                  * denza                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    =    01
                     go to pmt-app-scf-320
           else      go to pmt-app-scf-340.
       pmt-app-scf-320.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tipo Italia : 01                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "ABI              :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "CAB              :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "C/C [IBAN]       :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-app-scf-999.
       pmt-app-scf-340.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tipo Estero : 02                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "Banca estera     :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-app-scf-999.
       pmt-app-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 08                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "C/C Postale      :" to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
           go to     pmt-app-scf-999.
       pmt-app-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Tipo riga per scadenza fornitore     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-tri-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione valore di default              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if       (w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    spaces ) and
                    (w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    02    or
                     w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    03     )
                     move  "BB  "         to   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore precedente               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    to   w-sav-tri-scf          .
       acc-tri-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ripristino valore precedente                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-sav-tri-scf        to   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Parametri generici                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      04                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tasti funzione                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Up   : sempre ammesso                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Down : sempre ammesso a meno che non ci *
      *                      *        siano zero righe                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-co3    not  = spaces
                     move  "DOWN"         to   v-pfk (02)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Find : sempre ammesso                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "FIND"               to   v-pfk (03)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Insr : sempre ammesso, a meno che non   *
      *                      *        si sia in un record New oppure   *
      *                      *        manchi spazio per l'inserimento  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces and
                     w-cat-rg3-ins        =    spaces
                     move  "INSR"         to   v-pfk (04)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Do   : sempre ammesso, purche' sia con- *
      *                      *        cesso dallo status delle impo-   *
      *                      *        stazioni; eventualmente disat-   *
      *                      *        tivato dal richiamo della sub-   *
      *                      *        routine di accettazione          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-imp-tes    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-cor    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-te2    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-co2    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-co3    not  = spaces and
                     w-cnt-sts-imp-pie    not  = spaces
                     move  "DO  "         to   v-pfk (05)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Remv : sempre ammesso                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Prsc : sempre ammesso                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "PRSC"               to   v-pfk (07)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Nxsc : sempre ammesso                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "NXSC"               to   v-pfk (08)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Back : sempre ammesso, a meno che non   *
      *                      *        si sia gia' sulla prima riga     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac    not  = 1
                     move  "BACK"         to   v-pfk (09)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tab  : sempre ammesso, a meno che non   *
      *                      *        si sia gia' sull'ultima riga e   *
      *                      *        che questa sia in Append         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces or
                     w-cat-rg3-lst        =    spaces
                     move  "TAB "         to   v-pfk (10)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Slct : sempre ammesso, a meno che non   *
      *                      *        si sia gia' sull'unica riga      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-max        not  = 1
                     move  "SLCT"         to   v-pfk (11)             .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Valore di accettazione                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
       acc-tri-scf-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Richiamo subroutine di accettazione     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Return                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Find                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "FIND"
                     go to acc-tri-scf-250.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Find su tipi riga per scdenze fornitore     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   fnd-tri-scf-000      thru fnd-tri-scf-999        .
           if        w-fnd-tri-scf-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-100.
           move      w-fnd-tri-scf-tri    to   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)
                                               v-alf                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione tipo riga per scdenze for-  *
      *                  * nitore                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tri-scf-000      thru vis-tri-scf-999        .
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
           go to     acc-tri-scf-400.
       acc-tri-scf-250.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Slct                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "SLCT"
                     go to acc-tri-scf-300
           else      go to acc-tri-scf-350.
       acc-tri-scf-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Conversione numero riga impostato in forma- *
      *                  * to numerico                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      v-alf                to   w-cnt-slc-rap-alf      .
           move      zero                 to   w-cnt-slc-rap-num      .
           move      6                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           move      5                    to   w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
       acc-tri-scf-310.
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001      .
           if        w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001   =    zero
                     go to acc-tri-scf-320.
           if        w-cnt-slc-rap-chr
                    (w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001)   <    "0"   or
                     w-cnt-slc-rap-chr
                    (w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001)   >    "9"
                     go to acc-tri-scf-310.
           move      w-cnt-slc-rap-chr
                    (w-cnt-wrk-ctr-001)   to   w-cnt-slc-rap-cif
                                              (w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002)     .
           subtract  1                    from w-cnt-wrk-ctr-002      .
           go to     acc-tri-scf-310.
       acc-tri-scf-320.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se numero riga impostato minore di 1 o mag- *
      *                  * maggiore del massimo : reimpostazione       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-slc-rap-num    =    zero       or
                     w-cnt-slc-rap-num    >    w-cat-rg3-max
                     go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se numero riga impostato pari a numero riga *
      *                  * attuale : reimpostazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-slc-rap-num    =    w-cnt-co3-nrg-dac
                     go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione parametri e uscita             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cnt-slc-rap-num    to   w-cnt-slc-num-rig      .
           move      "."                  to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3      .
           go to     acc-tri-scf-999.
       acc-tri-scf-350.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Delt                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DELT"
                     move  "X"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se premuto un altro tasto funzione non deve es- *
      *              * sere avvenuta variazione del campo d'impostaz.  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-mod                not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Up                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     move  "U"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Down                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DOWN"
                     move  "D"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-nok-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-nok-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-nok-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-tri-scf-999
                     else    go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Insr                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "INSR"
                     move  "I"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Tab                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "TAB "
                     move  "T"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Back                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "BACK"
                     move  "B"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Nxsc                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "NXSC"
                     move  "N"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Prsc                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "PRSC"
                     move  "P"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-tri-scf-999.
       acc-tri-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se impostazione a vuoto                     *
      *                  *    - se in Append : come Down purche' non   *
      *                  *                     ci siano zero righe     *
      *                  *    - altrimenti   : reimpostazione          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-alf                =    spaces
                     if    w-cat-rg3-new  not  = spaces and
                           w-cat-rg3-lst  not  = spaces and
                           w-cnt-sts-imp-co3
                                          not  = spaces
                           move  "D"      to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                           go to acc-tri-scf-999
                     else  go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non e' uno dei tipi previsti si tratta   *
      *                  * come per il tasto Slct                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-alf                not  = "RD  " and
                     v-alf                not  = "IE  " and
                     v-alf                not  = "RIBA" and
                     v-alf                not  = "CDO " and
                     v-alf                not  = "MAV " and
                     v-alf                not  = "RID " and
                     v-alf                not  = "BB  " and
                     v-alf                not  = "CCP " and
                     v-alf                not  = "RB  " and
                     v-alf                not  = "TR  " and
                     v-alf                not  = "PC  "
                     go to acc-tri-scf-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se record non New non si ammette la modifi- *
      *                  * ca del valore                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces and
                     v-mod                not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tipo tipo documento CEE o Estero, il     *
      *                  * valore non puo' che essere : BB             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if       (w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    02 or
                     w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    03) and
                     v-alf                not  = "BB  "
                     go to acc-tri-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      v-alf                to   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)      .
       acc-tri-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se riga non New : oltre                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-new        =    spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione tipo scadenza fornitore      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "RD  "
                     move  01             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "IE  "
                     move  02             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "RIBA"
                     move  03             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "CDO "
                     move  04             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "MAV "
                     move  05             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "RID "
                     move  06             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "BB  "
                     move  07             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "CCP "
                     move  08             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "RB  "
                     move  09             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "TR  "
                     move  10             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else if   w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    =    "PC  "
                     move  11             to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)
           else      move  zero           to   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione tipo valuta scadenza forni-  *
      *                  * tore                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if       (w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    07    ) and
                    (w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    02 or
                     w-tes-cod-tmf-tpv    =    03  )
                     move  02             to   w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)
           else      move  01             to   w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione prompts per appoggio sca-   *
      *                  * denza                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-app-scf-000      thru pmt-app-scf-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione default per appoggio scadenza  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Deviazione in funzione del tipo scaden- *
      *                      * za                                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    01
                     go to acc-tri-scf-610
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    02 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    03 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    04 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    05 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    06
                     go to acc-tri-scf-620
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    07
                     go to acc-tri-scf-630
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    08
                     go to acc-tri-scf-640
           else if   w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    09 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    10 or
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    =    11
                     go to acc-tri-scf-620
           else      go to acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-610.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 01                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Nessun default                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-620.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 02, 03, 04, 05, 06, 09, 10   *
      *              *                    11                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Default per ns. banca d'appoggio            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura archivio [dcf]                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "C"                  to   w-let-arc-dcf-tle      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-dcf-cod      .
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-dpz      .
           perform   let-arc-dcf-000      thru let-arc-dcf-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non esistente : normalizza-   *
      *                      * zione codice e no preparazione default  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-flg    not  = spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)
                     go to acc-tri-scf-628.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Memorizzazione codice ns. banca         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-ban    to   w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se codice a spaces : no preparazione    *
      *                      * default                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)    =    spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-628.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura archivio [cbp]                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      02                   to   w-let-arc-cbp-tip      .
           move      w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)    to   w-let-arc-cbp-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-cbp-000      thru let-arc-cbp-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non esistente : normalizza-   *
      *                      * zione codice e no preparazione default  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-cbp-flg    not  = spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)
                     go to acc-tri-scf-628.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Memorizzazione descrizione              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-cbp-des    to   w-rg3-cbp-scf-des (1)  .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Visualizzazione codice e descrizione    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cbp-scf-000      thru vis-cbp-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-cbp-scf-des-000  thru vis-cbp-scf-des-999    .
       acc-tri-scf-628.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Oltre                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-630.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 07                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del tipo valuta      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    =    01
                     go to acc-tri-scf-632
           else      go to acc-tri-scf-636.
       acc-tri-scf-632.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tipo Italia 01 : default per codici ABI, *
      *                  * CAB e c/c                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura archivio [dcf] relativa al for- *
      *                      * nitore o alla sua dipendenza            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-dpz-arc (1)    =    spaces
                     move  "C"            to   w-let-arc-dcf-tle
           else      move  "D"            to   w-let-arc-dcf-tle      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-dcf-cod      .
           move      w-tes-dpz-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-dcf-dpz      .
           perform   let-arc-dcf-000      thru let-arc-dcf-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non esistente : no prepara-   *
      *                      * zione default                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-634.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se codice banca d'appoggio del forni-   *
      *                      * tore associata ai dati commerciali del  *
      *                      * fornitore a zero : no preparazione      *
      *                      * default                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-abi    =    zero
                     go to acc-tri-scf-634.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Preparazione default per codice ABI del *
      *                      * fornitore                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Lettura archivio [axi]              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-abi    to   w-let-arc-axi-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-axi-000      thru let-arc-axi-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se record non esistente : no prepa- *
      *                          * razione default                     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-axi-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-634.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Preparazione default codice ABI     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-abi    to   w-rg3-abi-scf (1)      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Memorizzazione denominazione        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-axi-den    to   w-rg3-abi-scf-den (1)  .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione codice ABI          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-abi-scf-000      thru vis-abi-scf-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione denominazione       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-abi-scf-den-000  thru vis-abi-scf-den-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Preparazione default per codice CAB del *
      *                      * fornitore                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se codice CAB a zero : no prepara-  *
      *                          * zione default per il codice CAB     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-cab    =    zero
                     go to acc-tri-scf-634.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Lettura archivio [axs]              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-abi    to   w-let-arc-axs-abi      .
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-cab    to   w-let-arc-axs-cab      .
           perform   let-arc-axs-000      thru let-arc-axs-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se record non esistente : no prepa- *
      *                          * razione default per il codice CAB   *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-axs-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tri-scf-634.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Preparazione default codice CAB     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-cab    to   w-rg3-cab-scf (1)      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Memorizzazione denominazione        *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-axs-den    to   w-rg3-cab-scf-den (1)  .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione codice CAB          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cab-scf-000      thru vis-cab-scf-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione denominazione       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cab-scf-den-000  thru vis-cab-scf-den-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Preparazione default per conto corrente *
      *                      * del fornitore                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Preparazione default conto corrente *
      *                          * del fornitore                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-ccc    to   w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione conto corrente del  *
      *                          * fornitore                           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ccc-scf-000      thru vis-ccc-scf-999        .
       acc-tri-scf-634.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Oltre                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-636.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tipo Estero 02 : nessun default          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Oltre                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-640.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo scadenza : 08                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Default per c/c postale                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura archivio [dcf]                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-dpz-arc (1)    =    spaces
                     move  "C"            to   w-let-arc-dcf-tle
           else      move  "D"            to   w-let-arc-dcf-tle      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-dcf-cod      .
           move      w-tes-dpz-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-dcf-dpz      .
           perform   let-arc-dcf-000      thru let-arc-dcf-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se record non esistente : normalizza-   *
      *                      * zione codice e no preparazione default  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-flg    not  = spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)
                     go to acc-tri-scf-648.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Memorizzazione c/c postale              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-ccp    to   w-rg3-ccp-scf (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Visualizzazione c/c postale             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ccp-scf-000      thru vis-ccp-scf-999        .
       acc-tri-scf-648.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Oltre                                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-800.
       acc-tri-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Tipo riga per scadenza fornitore  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tri-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      04                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-tri-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale tipo pagamento determinato da 'xml'   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tri-scf-xml-000  thru vis-tri-scf-xml-999    .
       vis-tri-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Tipo riga per scadenza fornitore  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per eventuale tipo pagamento da 'xml'          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tri-scf-xml-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se inserimento                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to vis-tri-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su nome file                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fil-sdi (1)    =    spaces
                     go to vis-tri-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su progressivo riga                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-cur        =    zero or
                     w-cat-rg3-cur        >    9
                     go to vis-tri-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo pagamento                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    spaces
                     go to vis-tri-scf-xml-900.
       vis-tri-scf-xml-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Decodifica tipo pagamento                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP01"
                     move  "RD"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP02"
                     move  "RD"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP03"
                     move  "RD"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP04"
                     move  "RD"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP05"
                     move  "BB"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP06"
                     move  "PC"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP07"
                     move  "MAV"          to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP08"
                     move  "RD"           to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP09"
                     move  "RID"          to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP10"
                     move  "RID"          to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP11"
                     move  "RID"          to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP12"
                     move  "RIBA"         to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else if   w-trd-scx-mod
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    "MP13"
                     move  "MAV"          to   w-all-str-cat (2)
           else      move  w-trd-scx-mod
                          (w-cat-rg3-cur) to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assemblaggio                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      06                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "("                  to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      ")"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      06                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      40                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-tri-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-tri-scf-xml-999.
       vis-tri-scf-xml-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Si/No pagamento bloccato             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-snx-pbl-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-snx-pbl-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "E"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-exp-snx-pbl-lun    to   v-car                  .
           move      w-exp-snx-pbl-num    to   v-ldt                  .
           move      "NS#"                to   v-msk                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-exp-snx-pbl-tbl    to   v-txt                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      78                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
      *
           if        w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    =    "N"
                     move  01             to   v-num
           else if   w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    =    "S"
                     move  02             to   v-num
           else      move  zero           to   v-num                  .
      *
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg2
                     go to acc-snx-pbl-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg2
                     go to acc-snx-pbl-999.
       acc-snx-pbl-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-num                =    01
                     move  "N"            to   w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)
           else if   v-num                =    02
                     move  "S"            to   w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)
           else      move  spaces         to   w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)      .
       acc-snx-pbl-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    not  = spaces and
                     w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    not  = "N"    and
                     w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    not  = "S"
                     go to acc-snx-pbl-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore a Spaces non ammesso, a meno che non *
      *                  * si sia in Up                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    not = spaces
                     go to acc-snx-pbl-600.
           if        v-key                =   "UP  "
                     go to acc-snx-pbl-600
           else      go to acc-snx-pbl-100.
       acc-snx-pbl-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-snx-pbl-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg2-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg2-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg2-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg2
                             go to acc-snx-pbl-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg2-flg
                             go to acc-snx-pbl-100.
       acc-snx-pbl-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Si/No pagamento bloccato          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-snx-pbl-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "E"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-exp-snx-pbl-lun    to   v-car                  .
           move      w-exp-snx-pbl-num    to   v-ldt                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-exp-snx-pbl-tbl    to   v-txt                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      78                   to   v-pos                  .
      *
           if        w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    =    "N"
                     move  01             to   v-num
           else if   w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    =    "S"
                     move  02             to   v-num
           else      move  zero           to   v-num                  .
      *
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-snx-pbl-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Data di scadenza                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-dts-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-dts-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      ">"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    to   v-dat                  .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-dts-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-dts-scf-999.
       acc-dts-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-dat                to   w-rg3-dts-scf (1)      .
       acc-dts-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-dts-scf-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test che, se la data di scadenza e' diversa *
      *                  * da zero, cioe' non a vista, essa non sia    *
      *                  * inferiore alla data documento               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    =    zero
                     go to acc-dts-scf-600.
           if        w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    not  < w-tes-dat-doc (1)
                     go to acc-dts-scf-600.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Messaggio di errore                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "La data scadenza non puo' essere inferiore alla da
      -              "ta documento ! "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Reimpostazione                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-dts-scf-100.
       acc-dts-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se data scadenza a vista : visualizzazione  *
      *                  * della dicitura                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to acc-dts-scf-800.
           perform   vis-dts-scf-000      thru vis-dts-scf-999        .
       acc-dts-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-dts-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-dts-scf-100.
       acc-dts-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Data di scadenza                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-dts-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda del valore della data di   *
      *              * scadenza                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    =    zero
                     go to vis-dts-scf-100
           else      go to vis-dts-scf-200.
       vis-dts-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se data di scadenza a zero, cioe' a vista       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      08                   to   v-car                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "A vista "           to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-dts-scf-999.
       vis-dts-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se data di scadenza diversa da zero             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-dts-scf (1)    to   v-dat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Eventuale data determinata da 'xml'         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-dts-scf-xml-000  thru vis-dts-scf-xml-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-dts-scf-999.
       vis-dts-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Data di scadenza                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per eventuale data da 'xml'                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-dts-scf-xml-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se inserimento                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to vis-dts-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su nome file                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fil-sdi (1)    =    spaces
                     go to vis-dts-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su progressivo riga                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-cur        =    zero or
                     w-cat-rg3-cur        >    9
                     go to vis-dts-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su data                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-dat
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    zero
                     go to vis-dts-scf-xml-900.
       vis-dts-scf-xml-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Editing data                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-trd-scx-dat
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       to   v-dat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assemblaggio                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      10                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "("                  to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      ")"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      10                   to   v-car                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      40                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-dts-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-dts-scf-xml-999.
       vis-dts-scf-xml-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Importo scadenza in valuta           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-iiv-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to acc-iiv-scf-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore precedente               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    to   w-sav-iiv-scf          .
       acc-iiv-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<GB"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           move      w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-iiv-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-iiv-scf-999.
       acc-iiv-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)      .
       acc-iiv-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore a zero : reimpostazione, a meno   *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to acc-iiv-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-iiv-scf-600
           else      go to acc-iiv-scf-100.
       acc-iiv-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore attuale come precedente : oltre   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    =    w-sav-iiv-scf
                     go to acc-iiv-scf-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione importo scadenza             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    to   w-cvs-vlt-sgl          .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   w-cvs-vlt-dec          .
           move      w-tes-tdc-vpf (1)    to   w-cvs-vlt-tdc          .
           move      w-tes-cdc-vpf (1)    to   w-cvs-vlt-cdc          .
           move      w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    to   w-cvs-vlt-aav          .
           perform   cvs-alt-vlb-000      thru cvs-alt-vlb-999        .
           move      w-cvs-vlt-avb        to   w-rg3-imp-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione importo scadenza            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-imp-scf-000      thru vis-imp-scf-999        .
       acc-iiv-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-iiv-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-iiv-scf-100.
       acc-iiv-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Importo scadenza in valuta        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-iiv-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to vis-iiv-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<GB"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-iiv-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Importo scadenza fornitore           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-imp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-imp-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      c-dec                to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<GB"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     move  20             to   v-pos
           else      move  45             to   v-pos                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           move      w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-imp-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-imp-scf-999.
       acc-imp-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-rg3-imp-scf (1)      .
       acc-imp-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-imp-scf-425.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore a zero : reimpostazione, a meno   *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to acc-imp-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-imp-scf-600
           else      go to acc-imp-scf-100.
       acc-imp-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Trattamento importo scadenza in valuta      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    not  = c-sgl
                     go to acc-imp-scf-800.
           move      w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    to   w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)      .
       acc-imp-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-imp-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-imp-scf-100.
       acc-imp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Importo scadenza fornitore        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-imp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      c-dec                to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<GB"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
      *
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     move  20             to   v-pos
           else      move  45             to   v-pos                  .
      *
           move      w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale importo determinat0 da 'xml'          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-imp-scf-xml-000  thru vis-imp-scf-xml-999    .
       vis-imp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Importo scadenza fornitore        *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per eventuale importo da 'xml'                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-imp-scf-xml-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se inserimento                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to vis-imp-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su nome file                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fil-sdi (1)    =    spaces
                     go to vis-imp-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su progressivo riga                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-cur        =    zero or
                     w-cat-rg3-cur        >    9
                     go to vis-imp-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su importo                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-imp
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    zero
                     go to vis-imp-scf-xml-900.
       vis-imp-scf-xml-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Editing importo                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      c-dec                to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<GB"                to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-trd-scx-imp
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assemblaggio                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      18                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "("                  to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      ")"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   v-car                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      40                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-imp-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-imp-scf-xml-999.
       vis-imp-scf-xml-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Codice nostra banca d'appoggio       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cbp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 02 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 03 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 04 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 05 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 06 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 09 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 10 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 11
                     go to acc-cbp-scf-999.
       acc-cbp-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   w-cod-des-cbp-ope      .
           move      02                   to   w-cod-des-cbp-tip      .
           move      w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)    to   w-cod-des-cbp-cod      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-des-cbp-lin      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-des-cbp-pos      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-des-cbp-dln      .
           move      31                   to   w-cod-des-cbp-dps      .
           move      spaces               to   v-edm                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "FIND"               to   v-pfk (03)             .
           move      "INSR"               to   v-pfk (04)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           perform   cod-des-cbp-cll-000  thru cod-des-cbp-cll-999    .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
           perform   cod-des-cbp-foi-000  thru cod-des-cbp-foi-999    .
       acc-cbp-scf-110.
           perform   cod-des-cbp-cll-000  thru cod-des-cbp-cll-999    .
           if        w-cod-des-cbp-ope    =    "F+"
                     go to acc-cbp-scf-115.
           if        w-cod-des-cbp-ope    =    "AC"
                     go to acc-cbp-scf-120.
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
       acc-cbp-scf-115.
           perform   cod-des-cbp-foi-000  thru cod-des-cbp-foi-999    .
           go to     acc-cbp-scf-110.
       acc-cbp-scf-120.
           move      w-cod-des-cbp-cod    to   v-alf                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-cbp-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-cbp-scf-999.
       acc-cbp-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-alf                to   w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)      .
       acc-cbp-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cbp-scf-410.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura archivio [cbp]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      02                   to   w-let-arc-cbp-tip      .
           move      w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)    to   w-let-arc-cbp-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-cbp-000      thru let-arc-cbp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Memorizzazione descrizione                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-cbp-des    to   w-rg3-cbp-scf-des (1)  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione descrizione                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cbp-scf-des-000  thru vis-cbp-scf-des-999    .
       acc-cbp-scf-430.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se record non esistente : reimpostazione    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-cbp-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cbp-scf-100.
       acc-cbp-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cbp-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-cbp-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-cbp-scf-100.
       acc-cbp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice nostra banca d'appoggio    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cbp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 02 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 03 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 04 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 05 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 06 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 09 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 10 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 11
                     go to vis-cbp-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      10                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-cbp-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-cbp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Descrizione nostra banca d'appog- *
      *    *                         gio                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cbp-scf-des-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 02 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 03 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 04 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 05 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 06 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 09 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 10 and
                     w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 11
                     go to vis-cbp-scf-des-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      31                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-cbp-scf-des (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-cbp-scf-des-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Codice ABI per scadenza fornitore    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-abi-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to acc-abi-scf-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore precedente               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-sav-abi-scf          .
       acc-abi-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   w-cod-mne-abi-ope      .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-cod-mne-abi-cod      .
           move      19                   to   w-cod-mne-abi-lin      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-mne-abi-pos      .
           move      19                   to   w-cod-mne-abi-dln      .
           move      31                   to   w-cod-mne-abi-dps      .
           move      "9B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "FIND"               to   v-pfk (03)             .
           move      "INSR"               to   v-pfk (04)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           perform   cod-mne-abi-cll-000  thru cod-mne-abi-cll-999    .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
           perform   cod-mne-abi-foi-000  thru cod-mne-abi-foi-999    .
       acc-abi-scf-110.
           perform   cod-mne-abi-cll-000  thru cod-mne-abi-cll-999    .
           if        w-cod-mne-abi-ope    =    "F+"
                     go to acc-abi-scf-115.
           if        w-cod-mne-abi-ope    =    "AC"
                     go to acc-abi-scf-120.
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
       acc-abi-scf-115.
           perform   cod-mne-abi-foi-000  thru cod-mne-abi-foi-999    .
           go to     acc-abi-scf-110.
       acc-abi-scf-120.
           move      w-cod-mne-abi-cod    to   v-num                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-abi-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-abi-scf-999.
       acc-abi-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-rg3-abi-scf (1)      .
       acc-abi-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-abi-scf-410.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura archivio [axi]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-let-arc-axi-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-axi-000      thru let-arc-axi-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Memorizzazione denominazione                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-axi-den    to   w-rg3-abi-scf-den (1)  .
       acc-abi-scf-420.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione denominazione               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-abi-scf-den-000  thru vis-abi-scf-den-999    .
       acc-abi-scf-430.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se record non esistente : reimpostazione    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-axi-flg    =    spaces
                     go to acc-abi-scf-440.
       acc-abi-scf-432.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Normalizzazione e visualizzazione co-   *
      *                      * dice CAB                                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    =    zero
                     go to acc-abi-scf-434.
           move      zero                 to   w-rg3-cab-scf (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rg3-cab-scf-den (1)  .
           perform   vis-cab-scf-000      thru vis-cab-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-cab-scf-den-000  thru vis-cab-scf-den-999    .
       acc-abi-scf-434.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * A reimpostazione                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-abi-scf-100.
       acc-abi-scf-440.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice a zero : reimpostazione, a meno   *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to acc-abi-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-abi-scf-600
           else      go to acc-abi-scf-100.
       acc-abi-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore attuale pari al valore precedente *
      *                  * : nessuna dipendenza                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    =    w-sav-abi-scf
                     go to acc-abi-scf-800.
       acc-abi-scf-650.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione e visualizzazione codice    *
      *                  * CAB                                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    =    zero
                     go to acc-abi-scf-675.
           move      zero                 to   w-rg3-cab-scf (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rg3-cab-scf-den (1)  .
           perform   vis-cab-scf-000      thru vis-cab-scf-999        .
           perform   vis-cab-scf-den-000  thru vis-cab-scf-den-999    .
       acc-abi-scf-675.
           go to     acc-abi-scf-800.
       acc-abi-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-abi-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-abi-scf-100.
       acc-abi-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice ABI per scadenza fornitore *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-abi-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to vis-abi-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale Codice ABI determinato da 'xml'       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-abi-scf-xml-000  thru vis-abi-scf-xml-999    .
       vis-abi-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice ABI per scadenza fornitore *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per eventuale Codice ABI da 'xml'              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-abi-scf-xml-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se inserimento                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to vis-abi-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su nome file                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fil-sdi (1)    =    spaces
                     go to vis-abi-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su progressivo riga                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-cur        =    zero or
                     w-cat-rg3-cur        >    9
                     go to vis-abi-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su Codice ABI                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-abi
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    zero
                     go to vis-abi-scf-xml-900.
           if        w-trd-scx-abi
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    w-rg3-abi-scf (1)
                     go to vis-abi-scf-xml-900.
       vis-abi-scf-xml-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Editing                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-trd-scx-abi
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assemblaggio                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      07                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "("                  to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      ")"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      10                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-abi-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-abi-scf-xml-999.
       vis-abi-scf-xml-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice ABI per scadenza fornito-  *
      *    *                         re, denominazione                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-abi-scf-den-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to vis-abi-scf-den-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      31                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf-den (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-abi-scf-den-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Codice CAB per scadenza fornitore    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cab-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to acc-cab-scf-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore precedente               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   w-sav-cab-scf          .
       acc-cab-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   w-cod-mne-cab-ope      .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-cod-mne-cab-abi      .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   w-cod-mne-cab-cab      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-mne-cab-lin      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-mne-cab-pos      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-mne-cab-dln      .
           move      31                   to   w-cod-mne-cab-dps      .
           move      "9B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "FIND"               to   v-pfk (03)             .
           move      "INSR"               to   v-pfk (04)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           perform   cod-mne-cab-cll-000  thru cod-mne-cab-cll-999    .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
           perform   cod-mne-cab-foi-000  thru cod-mne-cab-foi-999    .
       acc-cab-scf-110.
           perform   cod-mne-cab-cll-000  thru cod-mne-cab-cll-999    .
           if        w-cod-mne-cab-ope    =    "F+"
                     go to acc-cab-scf-115.
           if        w-cod-mne-cab-ope    =    "AC"
                     go to acc-cab-scf-120.
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
       acc-cab-scf-115.
           perform   cod-mne-cab-foi-000  thru cod-mne-cab-foi-999    .
           go to     acc-cab-scf-110.
       acc-cab-scf-120.
           move      w-cod-mne-cab-cab    to   v-num                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-cab-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-cab-scf-999.
       acc-cab-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-rg3-cab-scf (1)      .
       acc-cab-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cab-scf-410.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura archivio [axs]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-let-arc-axs-abi      .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   w-let-arc-axs-cab      .
           perform   let-arc-axs-000      thru let-arc-axs-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Memorizzazione denominazione                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-axs-den    to   w-rg3-cab-scf-den (1)  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione denominazione               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cab-scf-den-000  thru vis-cab-scf-den-999    .
       acc-cab-scf-430.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se record non esistente : a reimpostazione  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-axs-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cab-scf-100.
       acc-cab-scf-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice a zero : reimpostazione, a meno   *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to acc-cab-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-cab-scf-600
           else      go to acc-cab-scf-100.
       acc-cab-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore attuale pari al precedente : nes- *
      *                  * suna azione                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    =    w-sav-cab-scf
                     go to acc-cab-scf-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione codice IBAN                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-ibn-scf-000      thru vis-ibn-scf-999        .
       acc-cab-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-cab-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-cab-scf-100.
       acc-cab-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice CAB per scadenza fornitore *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cab-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to vis-cab-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale Codice CAB determinato da 'xml'       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-cab-scf-xml-000  thru vis-cab-scf-xml-999    .
       vis-cab-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice CAB per scadenza fornitore *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per eventuale Codice CAB da 'xml'              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cab-scf-xml-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se inserimento                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to vis-cab-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su nome file                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-fil-sdi (1)    =    spaces
                     go to vis-cab-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su progressivo riga                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rg3-cur        =    zero or
                     w-cat-rg3-cur        >    9
                     go to vis-cab-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su Codice CAB                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-trd-scx-cab
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    zero
                     go to vis-cab-scf-xml-900.
           if        w-trd-scx-cab
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    w-rg3-cab-scf (1)
                     go to vis-cab-scf-xml-900.
       vis-cab-scf-xml-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Editing                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-trd-scx-cab
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assemblaggio                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      07                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "("                  to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      v-edt                to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      ")"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      10                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-cab-scf-xml-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-cab-scf-xml-999.
       vis-cab-scf-xml-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice CAB per scadenza fornito-  *
      *    *                         re, denominazione                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cab-scf-den-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to vis-cab-scf-den-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      31                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf-den (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-cab-scf-den-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Conto corrente bancario per scadenza *
      *    *                      fornitore                            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-ccc-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to acc-ccc-scf-999.
           if        w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    =    zero or
                     w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    =    zero
                     go to acc-ccc-scf-999.
       acc-ccc-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           move      w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-ccc-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-ccc-scf-999.
       acc-ccc-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-alf                to   w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)      .
       acc-ccc-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-ccc-scf-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice a spaces : reimpostazione, a meno *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ccc-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ccc-scf-600
           else      go to acc-ccc-scf-100.
       acc-ccc-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-ccc-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-ccc-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-ccc-scf-100.
       acc-ccc-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Conto corrente bancario per sca-  *
      *    *                         denza fornitore                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-ccc-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to vis-ccc-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-ccc-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : IBAN per fattura fornitore        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-ibn-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to vis-ibn-scf-999.
           if        w-let-arc-fnt-naz    not  = "IT "
                     go to vis-ibn-scf-999.
       vis-ibn-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se presenti tutti gli elementi             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    =    zero or
                     w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    =    zero or
                     w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    =    spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-cod-cod-cin-edt
                     go to vis-ibn-scf-500.
       vis-ibn-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Verifica di congruenza sul codice CIN           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "VC"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-ope      .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-abi      .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-cab      .
           move      w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-ccc      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc-cin (1)
                                          to   w-cod-cod-cin-cod      .
           perform   cod-cod-cin-cll-000  thru cod-cod-cin-cll-999    .
           move      w-cod-cod-cin-cod    to   w-tes-cod-arc-cin (1)  .
       vis-ibn-scf-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione del CIN Europeo                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "VE"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-ope      .
           move      w-let-arc-fnt-naz    to   w-cod-cod-cin-naz      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc-cin (1)
                                          to   w-cod-cod-cin-cod      .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-abi      .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-cab      .
           move      w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-ccc      .
           move      "00"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-chd      .
           perform   cod-cod-cin-cll-000  thru cod-cod-cin-cll-999    .
           move      w-cod-cod-cin-chd    to   w-tes-cod-arc-ceu (1)  .
       vis-ibn-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione IBAN                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EI"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-ope      .
           move      "IT"                 to   w-cod-cod-cin-naz      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc-ceu (1)
                                          to   w-cod-cod-cin-chd      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc-cin (1)
                                          to   w-cod-cod-cin-cod      .
           move      w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-abi      .
           move      w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-cab      .
           move      w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    to   w-cod-cod-cin-ccc      .
           perform   cod-cod-cin-cll-000  thru cod-cod-cin-cll-999    .
       vis-ibn-scf-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Assemblaggio                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      32                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      "["                  to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      w-cod-cod-cin-edt    to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      "]"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione IBAN                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      30                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      40                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-ibn-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione eventuale segnale di differenza *
      *              * con l'IBAN indicato nel documento 'xml'         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Confronto codici IBAN                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cod-cod-cin-edt    =    spaces
                     go to vis-ibn-scf-900.
           if        w-trd-scx-ibn
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    spaces
                     go to vis-ibn-scf-900.
           if        w-trd-scx-ibn
                    (w-cat-rg3-cur)       =    w-cod-cod-cin-edt
                     go to vis-ibn-scf-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione segnale                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      34                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "!!!"                to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-ibn-scf-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-ibn-scf-999.
       vis-ibn-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Conto corrente postale per scadenza  *
      *    *                      fornitore                            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-ccp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 08
                     go to acc-ccp-scf-999.
       acc-ccp-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           move      w-rg3-ccp-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-ccp-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-ccp-scf-999.
       acc-ccp-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-alf                to   w-rg3-ccp-scf (1)      .
       acc-ccp-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-ccp-scf-450.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice a spaces : reimpostazione, a meno *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-ccp-scf (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ccp-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ccp-scf-600
           else      go to acc-ccp-scf-100.
       acc-ccp-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-ccp-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-ccp-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-ccp-scf-100.
       acc-ccp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Conto corrente postale per sca-   *
      *    *                         denza fornitore                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-ccp-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 08
                     go to vis-ccp-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-ccp-scf (1)    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-ccp-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Accettazione campo : Codice banca estera per scadenza     *
      *    *                      fornitore                            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       acc-bef-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 02
                     go to acc-bef-scf-999.
       acc-bef-scf-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione valore                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   w-cod-mne-bef-ope      .
           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-cod-mne-bef-dcf      .
           move      w-tes-dpz-arc (1)    to   w-cod-mne-bef-dpz      .
           move      w-rg3-bef-scf (1)    to   w-cod-mne-bef-cod      .
           move      19                   to   w-cod-mne-bef-lin      .
           move      20                   to   w-cod-mne-bef-pos      .
           move      19                   to   w-cod-mne-bef-dln      .
           move      31                   to   w-cod-mne-bef-dps      .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "FIND"               to   v-pfk (03)             .
           move      "INSR"               to   v-pfk (04)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      "REMV"               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           perform   cod-mne-bef-cll-000  thru cod-mne-bef-cll-999    .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
           perform   cod-mne-bef-foi-000  thru cod-mne-bef-foi-999    .
       acc-bef-scf-110.
           perform   cod-mne-bef-cll-000  thru cod-mne-bef-cll-999    .
           if        w-cod-mne-bef-ope    =    "F+"
                     go to acc-bef-scf-115.
           if        w-cod-mne-bef-ope    =    "AC"
                     go to acc-bef-scf-120.
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
       acc-bef-scf-115.
           perform   cod-mne-bef-foi-000  thru cod-mne-bef-foi-999    .
           go to     acc-bef-scf-110.
       acc-bef-scf-120.
           move      w-cod-mne-bef-cod    to   v-num                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-bef-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Remv                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "REMV"
                     move  "R"            to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                     go to acc-bef-scf-999.
       acc-bef-scf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-rg3-bef-scf (1)      .
       acc-bef-scf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controllo valore impostato                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura archivio [bef]                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-cod-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-bef-fnt      .
           move      w-tes-dpz-arc (1)    to   w-let-arc-bef-dpz      .
           move      w-rg3-bef-scf (1)    to   w-let-arc-bef-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-bef-000      thru let-arc-bef-999        .
           move      w-let-arc-bef-des    to   w-rg3-bef-scf-des (1)  .
           move      w-let-arc-bef-fil    to   w-rg3-bef-scf-fil (1)  .
           move      w-let-arc-bef-ccc    to   w-rg3-bef-scf-ccc (1)  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione dati banca estera           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-bef-scf-des-000  thru vis-bef-scf-des-999    .
           perform   vis-bef-scf-fil-000  thru vis-bef-scf-fil-999    .
           perform   vis-bef-scf-ccc-000  thru vis-bef-scf-ccc-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se lettura errata : reimpostazione          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-bef-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-bef-scf-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice a zero : reimpostazione, a meno   *
      *                  * che non si sia in Up                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-bef-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to acc-bef-scf-600.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-bef-scf-600
           else      go to acc-bef-scf-100.
       acc-bef-scf-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Dipendenze dall'impostazione                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-bef-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Do                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "DO  "
                     perform cnt-tdo-rg3-000
                                          thru cnt-tdo-rg3-999
                     if      w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-tus-acc-rg3
                             go to acc-bef-scf-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg
                             go to acc-bef-scf-100.
       acc-bef-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Codice banca estera per scadenza  *
      *    *                         fornitore                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-bef-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 02
                     go to vis-bef-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-bef-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-bef-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Descrizione banca estera          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-bef-scf-des-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 02
                     go to vis-bef-scf-des-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      19                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      31                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-bef-scf-des (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-bef-scf-des-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Filiale banca estera              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-bef-scf-fil-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 02
                     go to vis-bef-scf-fil-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      31                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-bef-scf-fil (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-bef-scf-fil-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : C/C banca estera                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-bef-scf-ccc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 02
                     go to vis-bef-scf-ccc-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      20                   to   v-car                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      31                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rg3-bef-scf-ccc (1)
                                          to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-bef-scf-ccc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Totale scadenze in valuta         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tiv-scf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se campo da visualizzare                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to vis-tiv-scf-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-tes-dec-vpf (1)    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<G"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-co3-tiv-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-tiv-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo : Totale scadenze fornitore         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tot-scf-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      c-dec                to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<G"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     move  20             to   v-pos
           else      move  45             to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-co3-tot-scf (1)    to   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-tot-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Controllo su impostazione tasto Do riga corpo             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-rg3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di uscita                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-rg3-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Controlli                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-rg3-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo scadenza fornitore                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-rg3-140.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data scadenza                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-rg3-160.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importo in valuta scadenza fornitore        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-180.
           if        w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-180.
           move      "Manca l'importo in valuta della scadenza          
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-180.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Importo scadenza fornitore                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-200.
           move      "Manca l'importo della scadenza                    
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Nostra banca d'appoggio per scadenza forni- *
      *                  * tore                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       cnt-tdo-rg3-220.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice ABI banca per scadenza fornitore     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-240.
           if        w-rg3-abi-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-240.
           move      "Manca il codice ABI della banca di appoggio per il
      -              " bonifico      "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-240.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice CAB sportello per scadenza fornitore *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-260.
           if        w-rg3-cab-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-260.
           move      "Manca il codice CAB della banca di appoggio per il
      -              " bonifico      "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-260.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * C/C bancario per scadenza fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 01
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-280.
           if        w-rg3-ccc-scf (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-280.
           move      "Manca la sigla C/C della banca di appoggio per il 
      -              "bonifico       "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-280.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * C/C postale per scadenza fornitore          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 08
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-300.
           if        w-rg3-ccp-scf (1)    not  = spaces
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-300.
           move      "Manca la sigla del C/C Postale di appoggio        
      -              "               "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Banca estera per scadenza fornitore         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-tip-scf (1)    not  = 07 or
                     w-rg3-tvl-scf (1)    not  = 02
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-320.
           if        w-rg3-bef-scf (1)    not  = zero
                     go to cnt-tdo-rg3-320.
           move      "Manca il codice banca estera di appoggio per il bo
      -              "nifico         "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-320.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Fine controlli, normalizzazioni                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione tipo operazione, causale e   *
      *                  * sottoconto per registrazione scadenza for-  *
      *                  * nitore                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-tcs-rsf-000      thru det-tcs-rsf-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Si/no pagamento bloccato                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)    not  = "N"
                     move  "S"            to   w-rg3-snx-pbl (1)      .
       cnt-tdo-rg3-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     cnt-tdo-rg3-999.
       cnt-tdo-rg3-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se controllo non superato                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Emissione messaggio di errore               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag di errore in uscita                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-tdo-rg3-flg      .
       cnt-tdo-rg3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Preparazioni pre-accettazione riga corpo 2                *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pre-rig-co3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio valori riga pre-accettazione        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    to   w-srp-iiv-scf          .
           move      w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    to   w-srp-imp-scf          .
       pre-rig-co3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Attribuzione del numero progressivo per la riga New       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       prg-rig-co3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Prelevamento da area di controllo catena        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rg3-prg        to   w-rg3-num-prg (1)      .
       prg-rig-co3-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Azioni post-accettazione riga corpo 2                     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pos-rig-co3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento totale in valuta scadenze fornitore *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da effettuare                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-sgl-vpf (1)    =    c-sgl
                     go to pos-rig-co3-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controaggiornamento                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-srp-iiv-scf        from w-co3-tiv-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiornamento, se necessario                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-tip-agg    not  = "+"
                     go to pos-rig-co3-250.
           add       w-rg3-iiv-scf (1)    to   w-co3-tiv-scf (1)      .
       pos-rig-co3-250.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tiv-scf-000      thru vis-tiv-scf-999        .
       pos-rig-co3-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento totale scadenze fornitore           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Controaggiornamento                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-srp-imp-scf        from w-co3-tot-scf (1)      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aggiornamento, se necessario                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-co3-tip-agg    not  = "+"
                     go to pos-rig-co3-750.
           add       w-rg3-imp-scf (1)    to   w-co3-tot-scf (1)      .
       pos-rig-co3-750.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-tot-scf-000      thru vis-tot-scf-999        .
       pos-rig-co3-999.
           exit.

